    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/3076bb9c76103b168988038e3d07a8ed.poster.avif?t=1764842232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/3076bb9c76103b168988038e3d07a8ed.webm?t=1764842232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/3076bb9c76103b168988038e3d07a8ed.mp4?t=1764842232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tears Apart is a fast paced action roguelite where your dash is your main weapon. Master the rhythm of attack and dodge to carve a path through the Chasm, where every run unlocks new powers and synergies.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The First Light in the Chasm </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Vane, your mission is to reach the heart of a ruptured cosmos before it drifts into the void entirely. Standing in your way is Shepard and his army of decay, determined to drag everything into eternal darkness.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat in Constant Motion </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vane's primary skill is Tear, a dash-strike that serves as both her main offense and her most reliable mobility tool. Master tears to both dodge enemy attacks and strike back with the right timing.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/cf633ebd995c99e4976d1b18c90dbad5.poster.avif?t=1764842232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/cf633ebd995c99e4976d1b18c90dbad5.webm?t=1764842232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/cf633ebd995c99e4976d1b18c90dbad5.mp4?t=1764842232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the Synergy </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strength comes from how well upgrades are arranged. Picking upgrades is only the first step. Equipping them in the right slots and aligning their effects is what creates real synergy. Experiment boldly to discover the builds that turn consecutive Tears into devastating combos and fully express unique playstyles.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/0e31e3b1098b3fa395cb6a1884b0a466.poster.avif?t=1764842232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/0e31e3b1098b3fa395cb6a1884b0a466.webm?t=1764842232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reclaim the Chasm From the Decay </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the Chasm, a procedural landscape of shifting, ruptured segments. Each attempt generates a new dungeon layout and new enemy formations. Battle various enemy sets and confront major bosses that stand as beasts of the Decay.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strength Forged Through Failure </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Failure is not the end; it’s the start of the next power spike. With each run, permanent stat upgrades, new features and world-altering systems increases the overall strength and diversifies future runs. Each death brings the journey closer to the truth and Vane to her destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/4737ccae5404aae65b058fca1ff8c06f.poster.avif?t=1764842232\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/4737ccae5404aae65b058fca1ff8c06f.webm?t=1764842232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166920/extras/4737ccae5404aae65b058fca1ff8c06f.mp4?t=1764842232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
